To build, either use opam:

    opam init
    opam remote add git://github.com/xen-org/opam-repo-dev
    opam install vxs

Or manually install the following dependencies:

    * Ocaml
    * obuild
    * camltemplate
    * cohttp
    * xen-api-client
    * cmdliner
    * ocamlify

and then type:

    make


